<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12805</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19566</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天早上，拇指姑娘正在做家务。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19567</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28283</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“慢慢扫地。”格雷夫人指正她，“要不然会有太多的灰尘。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28284</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38099</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后格雷夫人看着墙上的钟。她露出了奇怪的笑容。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38100</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43447</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然后门响起了短暂的敲门声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43448</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50133</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是洛夫斯先生！”格雷夫人打开了门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50134</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56243</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>洛夫斯先生是一只很大的，棕色的鼹鼠。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56244</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62265</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>像大多数鼹鼠一样，洛夫斯先生看得不是很清楚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62266</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以他戴着厚厚的眼镜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67424</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70888</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拄着拐杖走进了房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70889</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76196</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好，格雷夫人。”他用低沉的声音说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76197</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79862</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“感谢你邀请我来喝茶。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85359</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>格雷夫人笑了，声音比平时大了许多。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85379</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，洛夫斯先生，很高兴你能来。这是拇指姑娘。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102396</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>‘格雷夫人今天很奇怪。’拇指姑娘心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102397</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108658</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我去拿茶过来。”格雷夫人用甜美的声音说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108659</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115095</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“拇指姑娘留在这里和你聊天，洛夫斯先生。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115096</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120279</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她走的时候，格雷夫人小声对拇指姑娘说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120280</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129509</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“洛夫斯先生是一位很好的绅士。他还很有钱。要好好招待他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129510</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135829</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘坐在洛夫斯先生的旁边，他没有说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135830</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141071</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望冬天快点过去。”拇指姑娘说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141072</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147261</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“冬天永远都不够长。”洛夫斯先生嘟哝道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147262</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152332</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是冬天太冷了。”拇指姑娘说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152333</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158437</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我住的地方不冷。”洛夫斯先生继续嘟哝着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158438</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163511</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我住在这附近最深的洞里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163512</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169033</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那不是在很深的地下吗？你不能看到——，”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169034</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172780</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘看了看他的厚眼镜：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172781</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179938</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是说，你不能感受到阳光。或者听到鸟叫。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179939</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184600</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哼！”洛夫斯先生摆了摆手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184601</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190049</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁需要阳光？再说，那些鸟也很糟糕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190050</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194577</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们很麻烦。他们总是偷食物。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194578</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200498</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘想到了皮特，克里斯和麦琪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200499</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不同意您的想法，先生。”她说，“我有很多鸟类朋友。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213406</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们都非常善良。他们还教会我唱许多歌。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213407</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217482</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>洛夫斯先生把头转向拇指姑娘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217483</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221794</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那你唱一首。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221796</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226449</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不想唱。”拇指姑娘脸红了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226450</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230898</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哼！你是不会吧。”鼹鼠说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230899</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236595</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一点儿都不吃惊。鸟类没有好东西。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236596</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是的。”拇指姑娘说，“我给你唱一首歌。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247139</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘开始轻轻地唱歌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247140</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251887</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的声音逐渐升高，非常甜美。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251888</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257087</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她想起了她深深想念的玛丽戈尔德夫人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257088</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260955</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>洛夫斯先生的脸上露出微笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260956</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267441</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“成功了。”格雷夫人从厨房里偷偷看着他们说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267442</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272761</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>‘格雷夫人说得没错。’洛夫斯先生心想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272762</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>‘拇指姑娘的声音非常美妙。对，她一定能够成为我的好妻子。’</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286895</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘唱歌的时候没有想到鼹鼠和老鼠。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286896</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290214</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>歌声把她带回了家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290215</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308906</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是她一直不停地唱着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>